                        ©
                    REUTERS / Yonhap </span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="l-main m-oh"><div class="l-wrap m-clear"><div class="l-maincolumn m-static"><div class="b-article"><div class="b-article__refs-text "><a class="b-article__refs-rubric" href="/asia/" itemprop="articleSection">アジア</a><div class="b-article__refs-credits"><time class="b-article__refs-date" itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2020-02-04T00:41">2020年02月04日 00:41</time><time itemprop="dateModified" datetime="2020-02-04T03:11" class="b-article__refs-date-upd">(アップデート 2020年02月04日 03:11) </time><!--noindex--><span data-article="7072745" id="getShortUrl" data-shortUrl="" class="b-article__refs-getshorturl">短縮 ＵＲＬ</span><!--/noindex--></div><div class="b-article__refs-story"><div class="b-article__refs-story-label">トピック </div><div class="b-article__refs-story-title"><i class="b-icons b-icons_story"></i><a href="/trend/china-coronavirus/">新型コロナウイルス
